<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        function getParameterByName(name) {
            name = name.replace(/[\[]/, "\\\[").replace(/[\]]/, "\\\]");
            var regex = new RegExp("[\\?&]" + name + "=([^&#]*)"),
                results = regex.exec(location.search);
            return results == null ? "" : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, " "));
        }
        var ac = document.getElementById('allC');
        var homeImg = document.getElementById('homeImg');
        var city = getParameterByName('city');
        if (city == "") {
            ac.href = "AllCategories.aspx";
            homeImg.href = "Default.aspx";
        }
        else {
            ac.href = "AllCategories.aspx?city=" + city;
            homeImg.href = "Default.aspx?city=" + city;
        }
    });
</script>
